1
00:00:47,970 --> 00:00:50,160
Why is there an extra body?

2
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,120
Commissioner Di!

3
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,550
Did it scare you?

4
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,720
Scared to tears?

5
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:49,880
It was all...

6
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,120
It was entirely Master's idea.

7
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,200
Master even made me

8
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,880
dance the Nuo opera
to get your attention.

9
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,800
I don't know the first thing about it!

10
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,200
There are no signs

11
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:02,120
of struggle on the body,

12
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,760
meaning it was a single, fatal blow.

13
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:06,350
The victim has choke marks on the neck.

14
00:02:06,533 --> 00:02:08,040
Narrow on the left, wide on the right.

15
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,240
The attacker used their right hand.

16
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:12,840
To inflict both the fatal wound

17
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,520
and these choke marks

18
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,520
from the front, like Buyan here,

19
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:21,080
the killer would have to
choke with the right hand

20
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:23,320
and stab in reverse with the left.

21
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,022
That's peculiar.

22
00:02:24,066 --> 00:02:25,040
Too peculiar.

23
00:02:26,666 --> 00:02:28,640
So, the killer must have
struck from behind,

24
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,400
just like you.

25
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:32,980
Exactly.

26
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,440
The killer is left-handed.

27
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:54,940
=The Tang Mist S1=

28
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:15,580
=Episode 9=

29
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:18,020
(Gambling Parlor)

30
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:19,010
Small! Small! Small!

31
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:19,960
Get out!

32
00:04:20,130 --> 00:04:21,580
Broke and still trying to gamble?

33
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:22,500
Get lost!

34
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:23,280
Move it!

35
00:04:25,490 --> 00:04:26,360
Out of the way!

36
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,720
Don't ruin my luck!

37
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,790
Filthy drunkard!

38
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:33,650
No more bets!

39
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:37,720
Di,

40
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,400
Gu Qi lied to us.

41
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,280
Did Gu Pan'er have

42
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,840
any close friends when she was alive?

43
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,440
My Pan'er didn't really

44
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:46,140
have any friends.

45
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,950
Gu Pan'er wasn't without friends.

46
00:04:48,050 --> 00:04:49,210
She had a close confidante

47
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,170
named Dong Ling.

48
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:50,960
Duan,

49
00:04:51,530 --> 00:04:53,240
go keep a close eye on Gu Qi.

50
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,640
Again! Again!

51
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,240
Open!

52
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:55,680
Big!

53
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:58,440
- Open!
- Big! Big!

54
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,800
- (Gu Qi is a gambling addict.)
- Open! Open!

55
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,270
Open!

56
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,910
Any more bets?

57
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,120
Betting big or small?

58
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,400
Big! Big!

59
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,840
(I'm one myself.)

60
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,200
Big! Big! Big!

61
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:18,000
- Open! Open!
- Open!

62
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,600
Hey, you...

63
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,290
Open!

64
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:23,800
Open!

65
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,530
- Open!
- Open!

66
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,840
You win.

67
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,400
Again.

68
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:31,340
(Bets)

69
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,120
Big or small?

70
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,360
Big.

71
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,400
Big.

72
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:50,040
- Big!
- Big!

73
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,040
Why did you bet on small?

74
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,222
You won again.

75
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,520
I'm out of money!

76
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:05,440
It's all gone!

77
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,800
Do you even have cash?

78
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:14,080
Are you looking down on me?

79
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,000
Get lost.

80
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,400
Look at this.

81
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,000
A silver hairpin?

82
00:06:22,066 --> 00:06:23,520
You should have shown that earlier!

83
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,400
Hurry up!

84
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,320
Running away after winning?

85
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,040
This place is rigged!

86
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,640
Unless you cough up the money,

87
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,040
no one is leaving.

88
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,680
Get him!

89
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,560
Stop right there!

90
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,680
Catch him!

91
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,200
How am I already home?

92
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,360
Father.

93
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,880
You're back.

94
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,960
Pan'er...

95
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,520
Aren't you...

96
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,750
Father,

97
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:58,040
Mother is calling you home

98
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,790
for dinner.

99
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,200
Where is Gu Qi?

100
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:25,480
Darn you, Gu Qi!

101
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,360
You had me chasing you
like an eel all night!

102
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,840
I have never suffered

103
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:30,080
such indignity!

104
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,280
What are you doing?

105
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,160
Where are you going?

106
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:36,480
Why are you running?

107
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,640
Am I really that terrifying?

108
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:38,750
It has nothing to do with me!

109
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,244
- What do you mean?
- It wasn't me!

110
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:41,910
There's...

111
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,360
There's a dead body!

112
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,880
You're not going anywhere.
Stay right here and don't move!

113
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,080
Duan.

114
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,080
What happened?

115
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:53,800
I followed Gu Qi

116
00:08:53,820 --> 00:08:54,600
to the gambling den,

117
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,960
but I got distracted and lost him.

118
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,040
I searched all night,

119
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,440
only to find out he'd run back home.

120
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,288
By the time I found him,
he was already dead.

121
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,680
Have you forgotten why you were
dismissed from the army?

122
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,177
Exceptional hearing and agility.

123
00:09:05,190 --> 00:09:06,480
Put your talents to good use.

124
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,560
Why are you always gambling?

125
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,680
Sir.

126
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,520
Sir.

127
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,770
Gu Qi

128
00:09:26,810 --> 00:09:28,120
owes me a huge gambling debt.

129
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,680
I heard from the people at the den

130
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,800
that he actually
used a silver hairpin to bet.

131
00:09:32,050 --> 00:09:34,880
I figured he must have struck it rich,

132
00:09:34,933 --> 00:09:36,680
- so I came to collect.
- A silver hairpin?

133
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,220
But then...

134
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,920
A silver hairpin?

135
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,380
You should have shown that earlier.

136
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:43,760
The silver hairpin.

137
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,160
Duan, where are you going?

138
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,066
The silver hairpin.

139
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,000
Are you actually angry?

140
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:47,560
The hairpin

141
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,660
must be at the gambling den!

142
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,480
You know how it is.

143
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,320
Master values his cases
more than anything.

144
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:52,700
Lin,

145
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:53,670
do me a favor.

146
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,560
Name it.

147
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,800
Get that silver hairpin!

148
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,680
Who on earth is this guy?

149
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:11,120
You dirty old man.

150
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,080
Why are you here again?

151
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,880
It seems Master misjudged you.

152
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,555
You're addicted
to women, not gambling.

153
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:17,850
You can call me a lecher,

154
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,160
but don't you dare call me old.

155
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,200
Just so we're clear,

156
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,600
I don't hit women.

157
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:25,840
I will return
your money in full right away.

158
00:11:26,170 --> 00:11:28,010
Please calm your anger, Misters.

159
00:11:29,650 --> 00:11:31,000
Who wants your worthless silver?

160
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,480
I want the silver hairpin
from last night.

161
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:34,560
A silver hairpin?

162
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,080
Yes.

163
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,360
I...

164
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,320
I don't know about it.

165
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,800
Buyan.

166
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,040
Wreck the place.

167
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,160
Wait!

168
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,640
It's just a silver hairpin!

169
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,200
That's the one.

170
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,160
Gu Qi died inside a commode.

171
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,920
Rumors of the Guardian's curse

172
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,200
will only grow wilder now.

173
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:09,680
Talk of ghosts and gods

174
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,280
can blind the common people,

175
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:12,840
but it cannot hide the truth.

176
00:12:13,244 --> 00:12:15,480
His Majesty cares deeply
about the morale in Jiangnan.

177
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,920
If this spreads any further,

178
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,600
it will reach the capital from Raozhou.

179
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:20,800
Commissioner Di,

180
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,520
if His Majesty holds us accountable,

181
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:23,900
what are we to do?

182
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,400
With Commissioner Di here,

183
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,466
there is no need to fear.

184
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:31,360
No visible external injuries,

185
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,800
no signs of bleeding,

186
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,480
and no indications of poisoning.

187
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:39,000
His nose and mouth are clear.

188
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,720
He was stuffed
into the commode after he died.

189
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,040
His pupils are heavily dilated.

190
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,520
His face is twisted in horror.

191
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,320
He must have seen
something truly terrifying.

192
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,420
Was he scared to death?

193
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,720
Or perhaps a drug clouded his mind.

194
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:02,860
(Wangnian County Bureau)

195
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:06,220
Master.

196
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:09,440
Where is Duan?

197
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:10,920
Master,

198
00:13:11,410 --> 00:13:12,490
Duan said

199
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,280
he is too ashamed to face you.

200
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,040
If he doesn't quit gambling,

201
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,440
it will bring him ruin again.

202
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,340
Master,

203
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:20,733
to make amends for his mistake,

204
00:13:20,955 --> 00:13:22,640
he wants you to have
this silver hairpin.

205
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,200
Could this be

206
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,560
the weapon that killed Gu Pan'er?

207
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:27,680
And since

208
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,400
the hairpin was in Gu Qi's possession,

209
00:13:29,770 --> 00:13:30,780
is it possible

210
00:13:31,130 --> 00:13:32,920
that Gu Qi was the real killer?

211
00:13:34,111 --> 00:13:35,210
The footprints don't match.

212
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:36,880
Furthermore,

213
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,200
neither of them is left-handed.

214
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,320
(I've seen)

215
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:46,180
(this silver hairpin)

216
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,000
(on Dong Ling's head.)

217
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,920
(Except hers)

218
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,360
(had a tassel attached.)

219
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:58,020
(Hou Guangming, right-handed)

220
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,540
(Gu Qi, foot length,
23.3 cm, height, 171 cm)

221
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:01,180
(Dong Ling, silver hairpin)

222
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,540
(Mind-altering powder)

223
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:07,410
The killer's footprint is 27.33 cm.

224
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,420
And they are likely left-handed.

225
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,920
Every clue points directly to you.

226
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,200
Consumed by unrequited love

227
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,520
and bitter resentment,

228
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,440
you murdered her in a fit of rage,

229
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,022
along with the parents
who forced her to marry.

230
00:14:23,290 --> 00:14:25,440
It's a typical motive for murder.

231
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:27,040
Tell me,

232
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,310
why should I believe you?

233
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,520
I stand by what I said.

234
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,840
If you have hard evidence,

235
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:41,040
you are welcome to arrest me.

236
00:14:49,450 --> 00:14:50,980
Do you recognize this?

237
00:14:52,050 --> 00:14:53,000
It belongs to Pan'er.

238
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:58,400
This is the weapon that killed her.

239
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:02,960
Pan'er had a close friend

240
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,120
named Dong Ling.

241
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,360
Do you know her?

242
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:10,400
There is one thing I don't understand.

243
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:12,520
Since Pan'er was your friend,

244
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:15,000
and she met such a tragic end,

245
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,720
why haven't I seen you

246
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,640
show even a shred of grief?

247
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,000
The grief you speak of,

248
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,880
is it the kind worn on one's face?

249
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,920
As for mine,

250
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,640
I channeled it all

251
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,111
into my dance amidst the snow

252
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,520
during the Winter Festival.

253
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:35,920
Every step I take

254
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:37,120
carries my sorrow.

255
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,880
She was such a precious soul.

256
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,480
I want to share the beauty she left me

257
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,160
with the entire world.

258
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:45,880
If I could,

259
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,560
I would dance forever.

260
00:15:51,950 --> 00:15:54,220
The silver hairpin in your hair

261
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:55,688
is quite exquisite, Lady Dong Ling.

262
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,160
My mother gave it to me on her deathbed.

263
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,080
Was it a pair?

264
00:16:04,911 --> 00:16:06,200
It was supposed to be a pair.

265
00:16:07,022 --> 00:16:08,088
Where is the other one?

266
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,600
On the day of my mother's burial,

267
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:13,760
I gave it to Pan'er.

268
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,690
She is the only family

269
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,680
I have left in this world.

270
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:22,640
Is this the one?

271
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,720
Yes.

272
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,340
Where did you get it, sir?

273
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:33,730
From Gu Qi.

274
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:34,640
No.

275
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,000
Pan'er would never

276
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,080
give it to anyone else.

277
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:40,120
Perhaps someone stole it from her.

278
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,040
The tassel is missing.

279
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,160
The hairpin is no longer whole.

280
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:54,800
Sir, could you return it to me?

281
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,560
Once the case is resolved,

282
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,740
it will be returned
to its rightful owner.

283
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:09,640
Master.

284
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,120
Why didn't you mention

285
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,066
that Gu Pan'er was killed
by a silver hairpin?

286
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:15,480
This hairpin means

287
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,520
a great deal to Dong Ling.

288
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:19,000
If she knew Gu Pan'er died

289
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:21,320
from the very thing she gifted her,

290
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,670
I'm afraid...

291
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,440
Wait, no.

292
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:24,320
Master,

293
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:25,750
Dong Ling

294
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:28,040
gave the hairpin to Gu Pan'er on the day

295
00:17:28,040 --> 00:17:29,022
of her mother's burial.

296
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,670
Which was only a few days ago.

297
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,040
Go on.

298
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:34,360
But Zhuang Luobai claimed

299
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:36,480
he last saw Gu Pan'er over a month ago.

300
00:17:37,910 --> 00:17:39,400
How did Zhuang Luobai know the hairpin

301
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,520
belonged to Gu Pan'er?

302
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,640
So, what do you think?

303
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:44,970
Zhuang Luobai is lying.

304
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,080
Look at you.

305
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:47,840
You're finally making progress.

306
00:17:49,320 --> 00:17:51,520
Zhuang Luobai is deliberately concealing

307
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:53,600
the fact that he met with Gu Pan'er.

308
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,160
The truth behind her death

309
00:17:55,570 --> 00:17:57,480
must be hidden within this lie.

310
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,960
The noodles are getting cold.

311
00:18:01,390 --> 00:18:02,280
Come on out.

312
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:11,840
Di.

313
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:17,720
Sir.

314
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,540
Go tell Qinglan

315
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:28,640
to examine the victims' bodies

316
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,880
once more in greater detail.

317
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:33,140
Master.

318
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:35,160
Look how thrilled he is.

319
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:36,800
Buyan,

320
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:38,422
go keep a close eye on Hou Guangming.

321
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:39,880
Do you suspect him?

322
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,960
Among all of Gu Pan'er's relatives,

323
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,360
he is the only one left.

324
00:18:45,530 --> 00:18:47,840
Whether he is a victim or the killer,

325
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,360
the truth

326
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:51,050
is about to be revealed.

327
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:16,540
(Hou's Residence)

328
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,360
It's you.

329
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:55,580
(Preview of Next Episode)

330
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,720
If you don't practice hard,

331
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:59,000
you'll embarrass yourself on stage.

332
00:19:59,377 --> 00:20:01,577
If you perform
the God-Welcoming Dance this way,

333
00:20:01,644 --> 00:20:03,840
how can you be the lead dancer
for the Winter Festival?

334
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:06,730
My master is not the killer!

335
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:09,160
Please judge wisely, sir!

336
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:12,680
Zhuang Luobai didn't kill anyone!

337
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,160
Vice Director Hou,

338
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,760
regarding the deaths

339
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,920
of your wife, Pan'er, and her parents,

340
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:20,600
I have already unraveled the truth.

341
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,240
Would you care to hear it?

342
00:20:26,670 --> 00:20:28,250
♪Night covers the long streets♪

343
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:31,040
♪The city remains silent♪

344
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:34,020
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

345
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:36,520
♪Words still left unspoken♪

346
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,560
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

347
00:20:40,690 --> 00:20:43,160
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

348
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:45,260
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

349
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:48,400
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

350
00:20:49,020 --> 00:20:50,940
♪Love is born from desire♪

351
00:20:51,630 --> 00:20:53,760
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

352
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:56,560
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

353
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:59,860
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

354
00:21:01,310 --> 00:21:02,630
♪Someone once warned me♪

355
00:21:02,630 --> 00:21:04,150
♪To stop upon this shore♪

356
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:05,470
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

357
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:06,960
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

358
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,080
♪If one thought retreats♪

359
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,380
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

360
00:21:09,380 --> 00:21:10,720
♪But in this world♪

361
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:13,120
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

362
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:17,760
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

363
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:19,230
♪Still I walk ahead♪

364
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,680
♪Let it pierce through♪

365
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:25,420
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

366
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:27,660
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

367
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:29,060
♪Covering every heart♪

368
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,250
♪How many people♪

369
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:31,880
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

370
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:34,090
♪Yet call it♪

371
00:21:34,290 --> 00:21:35,630
♪Fate?♪

372
00:21:35,990 --> 00:21:37,170
♪Life and death♪

373
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:38,430
♪Balanced on a single line♪

374
00:21:38,780 --> 00:21:39,950
♪Light and shadow♪

375
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:41,210
♪Hanging side by side♪

376
00:21:41,210 --> 00:21:42,690
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

377
00:21:42,690 --> 00:21:44,100
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

378
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,640
♪In the end, it is only♪

379
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,020
♪A single misguided thought♪

380
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:48,580
♪If unveiling the truth♪

381
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:49,920
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

382
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,090
♪Then this answer♪

383
00:21:51,090 --> 00:21:52,450
♪Can it still remain true?♪

384
00:21:52,450 --> 00:21:53,850
♪When love and law♪

385
00:21:53,850 --> 00:21:55,330
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

386
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:56,730
♪Which figure before me♪

387
00:21:56,730 --> 00:22:03,930
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

388
00:22:03,930 --> 00:22:06,660
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

389
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:08,250
♪Still I walk ahead♪

390
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:09,490
♪Not for fame or glory♪

391
00:22:09,490 --> 00:22:14,360
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

392
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:16,170
♪Human nature is clouded♪

393
00:22:16,170 --> 00:22:17,890
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

394
00:22:17,890 --> 00:22:19,360
♪Though this world♪

395
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:20,730
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

396
00:22:20,730 --> 00:22:22,980
♪There is still a light♪

397
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:25,940
♪Worth pursuing♪

398
00:22:25,940 --> 00:22:27,760
♪Every case has its ending♪

399
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:29,020
♪But night does not always fade♪

400
00:22:29,290 --> 00:22:30,670
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

401
00:22:30,670 --> 00:22:31,890
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

402
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,240
♪If justice stands♪

403
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,490
♪Without mercy beside it♪

404
00:22:34,490 --> 00:22:36,290
♪Then how is it♪

405
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:45,850
♪Any different from a blade?♪

406
00:22:45,850 --> 00:22:49,040
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

407
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:50,520
♪Still I walk ahead♪

408
00:22:50,520 --> 00:22:51,910
♪Even if the world♪

409
00:22:51,910 --> 00:22:56,640
♪Refuses to answer♪

410
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,600
♪When every hidden truth♪

411
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:00,310
♪Finally reveals itself♪

412
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,670
♪I only wish♪

413
00:23:01,670 --> 00:23:03,150
♪To hold on♪

414
00:23:03,150 --> 00:23:07,890
♪Within the darkness♪

415
00:23:07,890 --> 00:23:09,890
♪To the heart♪

